        <td bgcolor='dimgray' valign='top' width='100%'><font color='white' face='Verdana, Arial, Helvetica' size='2'>Ok sitting here at work pondering the solo abilities with a bard vs a necro.</P><P>Now reason I ask this is because I know sometimes in the game I am stuck there without a group and would like the option to group AND solo.  I understand that at 28 bards get a fear song and at 23 bards get their snare song.  So there is the snare and fear technique.  Except the fact that it costs no mana.  Necros also have the same ability but costs mana also producing downtime</P><P>So no mana fear kite from bards = a lot less downtime.  Fear kite with necros = a lot more downtime.</P><P>Anyone that can add some more info please do.  I would like to hear opinions on this comparison to see viewpoints.</P><P><img src="http://taikoon.homestead.com/files/tai4.gif" border=0><BR><i>Sticking Feathers up your butt does not make you a chicken ~Tyler Durden</i><BR></font></td>
